latestPosts.caption:
Do you have any memories or images saved on your phone with your dad in a suit?

This Father’s Day, join Park Avenue’s Father’s Day contest:
1. Find or click a photo of you or your dad in a suit or shirt.
2. Share it on your Instagram Story using our ‘Add Yours’ template.
3. Tag @ParkAvenue and add a heartfelt note for your dad.

5 lucky winners will score ₹500 Park Avenue vouchers and a feature in our Story Highlights!

Get ready to post your entry on the ‘Add Yours’ Story by Park Avenue on June 15th!
